<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Grants advanced placement and credit to students who obtain a score of 3 or better in advanced placement examinations administered by the College Entrance Examination Board.  Test results in Biology, Chemistry and Computer Science will be evaluated for possible credit by the appropriate department Chair persons.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.saintpeters.edu/academics/catalogs/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
